#include <iostream>
#include <vector>
#include <string>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int n;
    cin >> n;
    vector<string> board(n);
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        cin >> board[i];
    }
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
            if (board[i][j] == '0') {
                board[i][j] = '6';
            }
            else {
                board[i][j] = '0';
            }
        }
    }
    for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
        for (int j = 0; j < n; j++) {
            cout << board[i][j];
        }
        cout << endl;
    }
    return 0;
}

def solution(board):
    # write your code in Python 3.6
    for i in range(len(board)):
        for j in range(len(board[i])):
            if board[i][j] == 0:
                continue
            else:
                if i == 0:
                    if j == 0:
                        board[i][j] = 1
                    elif j == len(board[i]) - 1:
                        board[i][j] = 2
                    else:
                        board[i][j] = 3
                elif i == len(board) - 1:
                    if j == 0:
                        board[i][j] = 4
                    elif j == len(board[i]) - 1:
                        board[i][j] = 5
                    else:
                        board[i][j] = 6
                else:
                    if j == 0:
                        board[i][j] = 7
                    elif j == len(board[i]) - 1:
                        board[i][j] = 8
                    else:
                        board[i][j] = 9
    return board
